  <h3>TL;DR, Our pick for Indian freelancers</h3>
  <p>Start with <strong>Claude (free)</strong> for writing, research, and client work. Add <strong>Canva Pro (₹500/month)</strong> for visuals, and <strong>Notion (free)</strong> for project management. Three tools, ₹500/month total, enough to handle 80% of freelance work in India.</p>
